      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FOR MERCY SAKE (2) has been hard to follow lately, running sixth (24.10) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Safe beginner and drawn well close to the inside. Better than latest and can atone here. STEELY DAWN (7) is yet to miss the placings in an excellent record this trip which boasts four wins and five placings. Placed last time (23.79) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing third and beaten 3 lengths. Looks one of the chances. TONY TARKS (1) comes off an average run last start when sixth at Grafton over 350m behind Love This Bar (20.72) in a Grade 5. A big run wouldn't surprise. GRANDPA JOE (8) is another with top-three prospects.",
